# Third-party and runtime dependencies

## RT-DETR HG (rtdetr-l / rtdetr-x)

VisionFramework ships a **standalone PyTorch** implementation of the Ultralytics RT-DETR HG topology
(HGStem / HGBlock / PAN / AIFI / RepC3 / RTDETRDecoder) so that **inference does not require the
`ultralytics` package**.

Official pretrained checkpoints published by Ultralytics (e.g. `rtdetr-l.pt`, `rtdetr-x.pt`) are
subject to **AGPL-3.0** (https://github.com/ultralytics/ultralytics). If you use those weights,
comply with the Ultralytics license in addition to this project’s `LICENSE`.

Optional: install `ultralytics` (e.g. `pip install -e ".[rtdetr-verify]"`) to run tests that
bit-compare against `RTDETRDetectionModel` from that package.

The rest of VisionFramework remains under the license stated in `LICENSE` / `pyproject.toml`.
